Score a URL for security risk

Usage: tirith score [OPTIONS] <URL>

Arguments:
  <URL>  URL to score

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format (default: human) [possible values: human, json]
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  tirith score https://get.example-tool.sh
  tirith score --format json https://example.com
